_struct_biol.details   
;ANALYSIS USING PISA SUGGESTS HUMAN ARP8 TO FORM A DIMER. AND THE CALCULATED PUTATIVE DIMER FORMATION IS DISCUSSED IN THE MANUSCRIPT SERVING A PRIMARY CITATION. HOWEVER, AS DISCUSSED IN THIS ACCOMPANYING MANUSCRIPT, THE DIMER FORMATION MIGHT BE INDUCIBLE IN VIVO AND/OR TRANSIENT, BUT DOES NOT SEEM TO STABLY OCCUR IN SOLUTION AS DEDUCED BY SAXS AND SLS EXPERIMENT
